/www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPxalLMq_gqw&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=c03aa07d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw</a><br />\n<br />\n呢次講吓意志力, 由生理角度提升意志力的方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4cN0cWQtB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg4cN0cWQtB0&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=156923cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4cN0cWQtB0</a><br />\n<br />\n呢次講吓目標清單及蔡格尼效應間的關係, 以此引伸目標清單的缺點<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y8l64NcUqjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY8l64NcUqjc&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=1aeff0fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y8l64NcUqjc</a>"},{"pid":"8c3d85777155c7e15a9e182a9e15322e67d1952d","tid":1008271,"uid":78029,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港歷史系列</strong>:<br />\n<br />\n呢集聚焦去睇東江水同香港供水系統如何生成, 從而拆解東江水係中國恩賜之類講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GiPkDPg7d04\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGiPkDPg7d04&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=df74cbd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GiPkDPg7d04</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集聚焦去冷戰初期50年代的時勢點令到港英政府成立香港中文大學<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0GfzPr1IcvA&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=17ea53c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GfzPr1IcvA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢集講吓教科書唔會教的香港歷史, 例如未開埠前有香港人幫英軍補給, 香港人唔係大中華史觀講到咁愛國 <img src=\